HEADWORD: Floriken
<hw>Flo"ri*ken</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>An Indian bustard (<spn>Otis aurita</spn>). The Bengal floriken is
<spn>Sypheotides Bengalensis</spn>.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>florikan</asp>, <asp>florikin</asp>,
<asp>florican</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Florilege</ent>⟦br⟧
